parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power windows can cause inconvenience, discomfort, and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Power windows do not roll up or down
power windows get stuck
power windows make unusual noises
power windows do not respond to switches.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield defroster can impair the driver's visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: Windshield defroster does not clear fog or ice
windshield defroster blows cold air
windshield defroster makes unusual noises
windshield defroster does not turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper blades can impair the driver's visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: Windshield wiper blades do not clear water or debris
windshield wiper blades leave streaks or residue
windshield wiper blades make unusual noises
windshield wiper blades do not move or are stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause a loss of brake function, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden loss of brake pressure
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal travels further than usual
vehicle takes longer to stop
or complete loss of braking ability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can lead to a reduced ability to alert other drivers or pedestrians of the vehicle's presence, potentially increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The horn does not sound when the horn button is pressed
the horn sounds weak or intermittent
the horn is inoperable
the horn button is stuck or difficult to press.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt does not latch or unlatch properly
the seat belt is stuck in the retracted position
the seat belt webbing is damaged or frayed
the seat belt buckle is broken or malfunctioning
the seat belt warning light is illuminated on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission housing leaks can cause the transmission fluid to drain, leading to overheating, premature wear, and eventual failure of the transmission, which can result in costly repairs, loss of vehicle control, and accidents.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaks from the transmission housing
transmission fluid drips onto the ground
the transmission slips or hesitates
the transmission makes unusual noises
the vehicle experiences difficulty shifting gears
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard.
